<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registry — Celebrating the Giglios</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@200;300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon-black.png" type="image/png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)">
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon-white.png" type="image/png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)">

    <style>
        /* Custom Styles & Parallax Engine for Registry Page */
        .registry-hero {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 75vh; /* Slightly taller to give the beautiful quote paragraphs breathing room */
            width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 140px 20px 80px 20px;
            background-color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .registry-parallax-bg {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 75vh;
            /* You can change 'registry-hero.jpg' to 'hero-bg.jpg' if you want to reuse the home page photo! */
            background: url('registry-hero.jpg') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
            z-index: 0;
            animation: registryImageScale 2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1) forwards;
        }

        @media (pointer: coarse) {
            .registry-parallax-bg { position: absolute; }
        }

        .registry-hero-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.5); /* Slightly darker overlay to ensure white text is highly readable */
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .registry-hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            color: #ffffff;
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* Elegant serif text styling matching your screenshot design */
        .registry-message-top {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.65rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.6;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .registry-message-bottom {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.65rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.6;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        /* Main solid section blocking out the parallax layer below it */
        .registry-main-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            background-color: #faf9f6;
            padding: 100px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .registry-section-title {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #dfb76c; /* Elegant gold header */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .registry-intro-text {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #555555;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Gold Registry Button Grid */
        .registry-links-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 25px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .registry-button {
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 220px;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #dfb76c;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 500;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(223, 183, 108, 0.15);
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }

        .registry-button:hover {
            background-color: #c9a054;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(223, 183, 108, 0.3);
        }

        @keyframes registryImageScale {
            from { transform: scale(1.08); }
            to { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* Responsive Breakpoints */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .registry-hero { min-height: 85vh; padding-top: 120px; }
            .registry-message-top, 
            .registry-message-bottom { font-size: 1.3rem; }
            .registry-links-grid { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
            .registry-button { width: 100%; max-width: 280px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="home" class="active">Home</a>
            <a href="story">Our Story</a>
            <a href="schedule">Schedule</a>
            <a href="travel">Travel & Stay</a>
            <a href="registry">Registry</a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-logo">
            <a href="index.html">
                <img src="wedding-logo.png" alt="Daryl and Mara Wedding Logo" class="logo-image">
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-rsvp">
            <a href="https://mararugen.com/wedding-rsvp" target="_blank" class="rsvp-top-button">RSVP</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="registry-hero">
        <div class="registry-parallax-bg"></div>
        <div class="registry-hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="registry-hero-content">
            <p class="registry-message-top">
                Many of you are traveling a distance to come celebrate with us. Your presence is gift enough! If you would still like to give a gift for our marriage, we welcome any marriage advice, encouraging scripture, your favorite books for marriage, a go-to recipe, etc.
            </p>
            <p class="registry-message-bottom">
                We are building a life on the solid rock and look forward to growing closer to God and each other every day. We are so thankful to you, our family and friends, for your support and encouragement in our marriage.
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="registry-main-content">
        <h2 class="registry-section-title">Our Registries</h2>
        <p class="registry-intro-text">
            For physical gifts or honeymoon contributions, we have compiled our registries below. Thank you so much for your love and support!
        </p>

        <div class="registry-links-grid">
            <a href="#" target="_blank" class="registry-button">View Zola Registry</a>
            <a href="#" target="_blank" class="registry-button">View Target Registry</a>
            <a href="#" target="_blank" class="registry-button">Honeymoon Fund</a>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
